  "sections": [
    {
      "selector": "section",
      "type": "hero",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 96,
      "width": 1920,
      "height": 630,
      "heading": "Your relationship starts with who you are.",
      "backgroundColor": "#080E1D",
      "callsToAction": [
        "IndividualPersonal Growth Assessment10 dimensions · R600 · 2",
        "CouplesRelationship Growth Assessment8 dimensions · R600 · 3"
      ],
      "text": "247 PEOPLE CHOSE HOW TO LOVE BETTER THIS YEAR... Your relationship starts with who you are. Two clinical-grade assessments. One for the individual who wants to understand their relational wiring. One for the couple who's done guessing. INDIVIDUAL Personal Growth Assessment 10 dimensions · R600 · 20–30 min COUPLES Relationship Growth Assessment 8 dimensions · R600 · 30–40 min Instant results · 100% private · Clinical-grade accuracy",
      "layout": "centered",
      "assetUrls": []
    },
    {
      "selector": "section",
      "type": "content",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 922,
      "width": 1920,
      "height": 882,
      "heading": "Which assessment is for you?",
      "backgroundColor": "#080E1D",
      "callsToAction": [
        "Begin →"
      ],
      "text": "TWO PATHS. ONE PRACTICE. Which assessment is for you? INDIVIDUAL Personal Growth Assessment R600 One-time For the person who knows something isn't working in their love life but can't quite name it. 10 dimensions of your relational self — clinically mapped, personally interpreted. Attachment Style — your neurological blueprint Trauma History — ACE-informed screening Emotional Regulation — your nervous system capacity Self-Worth & Identity — the foundation of everything Relationship Readiness — are you actually available? Communication Style — what's really happening Values & Life Vision — your",
      "layout": "centered",
      "assetUrls": []
    },
    {
      "selector": "#how-it-works",
      "type": "content",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 1804,
      "width": 1920,
      "height": 487,
      "heading": "How it works",
      "backgroundColor": "#080E1D",
      "callsToAction": [],
      "text": "SIMPLE. RIGOROUS. INSTANT. How it works 01 Choose your assessment Individual or couples. Complete the multi-step clinical form at your own pace — designed to be honest, not comfortable. 02 Answer 10 clinical dimensions From attachment wiring to trauma history to values alignment — each question is grounded in peer-reviewed research. 03 Receive your clinical report Instantly. A full Brown University-style PDF with scores, insights, clinical flags, and a personalised treatment pathway.",
      "layout": "centered",
      "assetUrls": []
    },
    {
      "selector": "section",
      "type": "content",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 2291,
      "width": 1920,
      "height": 559,
      "heading": "What people are saying",
      "backgroundColor": "#080E1D",
      "callsToAction": [],
      "text": "REAL RESULTS What people are saying ★ ★ ★ ★ ★ COUPLES “We were on the verge of separation. The report gave us a language to talk about what was actually broken — and a clear path to fix it.” Thandiwe & Sipho Johannesburg Now 18 months stronger ★ ★ ★ ★ ★ COUPLES “Worth every rand. Our couples therapist said it was the most useful intake tool she'd ever seen. We skipped months of guesswork.” Lerato & James Durban Saved 6+ therapy sessions ★ ★ ★ ★ ★ INDIVIDUAL “I thought I was ready for a relationship. This assessment showed me I had one dimension completely unaddressed. I'm grateful I did this b",
      "layout": "centered",
      "assetUrls": []
    },
    {
      "selector": "section",
      "type": "content",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 2849,
      "width": 1920,
      "height": 506,
      "heading": "Most couples wait 6 years before getting help.",
      "backgroundColor": "#080E1D",
      "callsToAction": [],
      "text": "THE COST OF WAITING Most couples wait 6 years before getting help. By then, resentment has calcified. Patterns have cemented. And you're spending R1,500–R2,000 per therapy session just figuring out what the problem is. Our assessments do that work in 30 minutes — so you can walk into any session already knowing. Same argument, different day. You're stuck in the loop. Disconnected but can't explain why. You keep choosing the wrong person.",
      "layout": "centered",
      "assetUrls": []
    },
    {
      "selector": "section",
      "type": "content",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 3356,
      "width": 1920,
      "height": 613,
      "heading": "What's inside your report",
      "backgroundColor": "#080E1D",
      "callsToAction": [],
      "text": "CLINICAL DEPTH. REAL ANSWERS. What's inside your report Overall Growth Score A weighted composite score with a visual gauge and contextual interpretation. Radar & Bar Charts Research-grade visual charts of all dimensions for immediate pattern recognition. Clinical Flags High/medium/low severity flags with specific recommendations for each issue found. 3-Phase Treatment Plan Session-by-session recommendations with pricing for a full clinical pathway. Deep Domain Analysis Neuroscience-informed interpretation of every dimension in plain language. Journal Prompts & Action Items Pre-session prompts",
      "layout": "centered",
      "assetUrls": []
    },
    {
      "selector": "section",
      "type": "content",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 3968,
      "width": 1920,
      "height": 591,
      "heading": "Simple. Worth it.",
      "backgroundColor": "#080E1D",
      "callsToAction": [
        "Take the Assessment →"
      ],
      "text": "TRANSPARENT PRICING Simple. Worth it. Compare that to R1,500–R2,000 per therapy session, just to figure out what to work on. INDIVIDUAL R600 10 clinical dimensions Personal growth score Clinical flags & insights 3-phase treatment pathway Full PDF report Love language + Attachment profile Take the Assessment → COUPLES R600 8 clinical domains Partner comparison charts Alignment percentage per domain ACE + ADHD screening Clinical risk matrix 3-phase couples pathway Take the Assessment →",
      "layout": "centered",
      "assetUrls": []
    },
    {
      "selector": "section",
      "type": "content",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 4559,
      "width": 1920,
      "height": 431,
      "heading": "The Uncommon Practice",
      "backgroundColor": "#080E1D",
      "callsToAction": [
        "Read the essays"
      ],
      "text": "KNOWLEDGE FIRST The Uncommon Practice 10 extensive essays on love, neuroscience, and what actually makes relationships work — written by Hakeem with the rigour of a researcher and the voice of someone who's seen it all. Read the essays",
      "layout": "centered",
      "assetUrls": []
    },
    {
      "selector": "section",
      "type": "content",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 4990,
      "width": 1920,
      "height": 628,
      "heading": "Questions",
      "backgroundColor": "#080E1D",
      "callsToAction": [
        "Who are these assessments for?",
        "Is this a replacement for therapy?",
        "How long does each assessment take?",
        "What if my results show serious issues?",
        "Is my data private?"
      ],
      "text": "Questions Who are these assessments for? Is this a replacement for therapy? No — it's the ideal starting point. Our reports give you (and your therapist) a clinical-grade GPS. Most therapists say it saves 4–8 sessions of discovery work. How long does each assessment take? What if my results show serious issues? Is my data private?",
      "layout": "centered",
      "assetUrls": []
    },
    {
      "selector": "section",
      "type": "content",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 5618,
      "width": 1920,
      "height": 427,
      "heading": "The LOVEBetter Newsletter",
      "backgroundColor": "#080E1D",
      "callsToAction": [
        "Join LOVEBetter"
      ],
      "text": "FREE · VALUABLE · HONEST The LOVEBetter Newsletter Neuroscience, attachment theory, and hard-won insights on love — delivered bi-weekly by Hakeem. No fluff. No algorithm. Just the real work. Join LOVEBetter",
      "layout": "centered",
      "assetUrls": []
    },
